<TEXT>
<P>
What a relief it was to see The Times give front-page treatment to Nelson's 
analysis of the major problem facing our nation -- preparing for the 21st 
Century. 
</P>
<P>
For years we have witnessed the deterioration of the systems which provide 
sustenance and support for the children of this nation, namely, education and 
health care. 
</P>
<P>
