<HEADLINE>
<P>
COLLEGE BASEBALL; 
</P>
<P>
MIKE ROBERTSON'S FIVE RBIS LEAD USC TO 7-5 VICTORY OVER UCLA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mike Robertson went four for four, including two home runs, and drove in five 
runs to lead USC to a 7-5 victory over UCLA in a Pacific 10 Southern Division 
game Sunday at Dedeaux Field. 
</P>
<P>
Robertson hit a three-run homer in the second inning and a solo shot in the 
fifth to increase his season total to seven. 
</P>
<P>
