</P>
<P>
Winner Jackie Nickell (5-2) came on in the sixth, giving up three hits and 
striking out five in three innings. The loser was starter Tim Lindsay (6-6). 
</P>
<P>
The Trojans, who won two of three from the Bruins during the weekend series, 
improved to 34-17 overall and 17-10 in the Southern Division. UCLA is 32-17 and 
14-16. 
