From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Entertainer Sammy Davis Jr., in failing health in a battle with throat cancer, 
was resting at home seven weeks after his release from a hospital, his 
publicist said. 
</P>
<P>
