<TEXT>
<P>
Hugh Hefner was relegated to the waiting room while the Playboy founder's wife, 
Kimberly Conrad, was giving birth to their first child. 
</P>
<P>
"Kimberly didn't want me in the delivery room, and I didn't really want to be 
there," Hefner, 64, said in the May 7 issue of People magazine. "She just felt 
it was a time of embarrassment. She's a very private person." 
